    <briefdescription>
<para>Deferred work queue — ISR-safe function dispatch. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>ISRs push work items (function + context) into a lock-free ring. The main loop drains the queue by calling <ref refid="syn__workqueue_8h_1a159723032296a26e12734817350fff37" kindref="member">syn_workqueue_process()</ref>.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Usage</title><para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="structSYN__WorkItem" kindref="compound">SYN_WorkItem</ref><sp/>items[8];</highlight></codeline>
