<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="syn__workqueue_8c_1aa21f36ebf0f10cc13bd62e2a55d34264" kindref="member">syn_workqueue_post</ref>(&amp;wq,<sp/>my_handler,<sp/>my_data);</highlight></codeline>
